      WILLIAM CUBITT
, Esq. M.P. Lord Mayor of the City of London; 


   Sir George Bramwell, Knt. one of the Barons of Her Majesty's Court of Exchequer; 


   Sir Charles Crompton, Knt. one of the Justices of Her Majesty's Court of Queen's Bench; 


   Sir John Musgrove, Bart.; 


   Thomas Challis, Esq.; 


   David Salomons, Esq. M.P. Aldermen of the said City; 


   Russell Gurney, Esq. Q.C. Recorder of the said City; 


   Sir Henry Muggeridge,. Knt; 


   Benjamin Samuel Phillips, Esq.; 


   John Joseph Mechi, Esq.; 


   Edward Conder, Esq.; and 


   Thomas Dakin, Esq., Aldermen of the said City; 


   Thomas Chambers, Esq. Q.C. common Serjeant of the said City; and 


   Robert Malcolm Kerr, Esq. Judge of Sheriffs' Court; Her Majesty's Justices of Oyer and Terminer and General Gaol Delivery of Newgate, holden for the said City, and Judges of the Central Criminal Court.
